{"tid":108870,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手]喺屋企搵到部yashica mg-1","createTime":"2017-02-05T14:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T14:05:45.000Z","uid":2258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d59a14c592d655cbe76425bbd79cdf3bf25a562","tid":108870,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"執屋嗰時 喺屋企執到部yashica mg-1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n部機係老豆細個嗰時 爺爺為左帶一家人去玩特登買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網搵左可以用一粒LR44+CR123A 代替停左產嘅原裝電<br />\n但係盞測光燈唔著<br />\n唔知係粒電唔啱定壞左<br />\n想問巴絲 應該買卷菲林試定拎去整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果整嘅話有無介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次接觸菲林機<br />\n好想可以用到依部機"},{"pid":"e206f9514b3635d193eda0c5a7be3c218d0b9ca3","tid":108870,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/225023_342d9920b474b2acd20c011c74bdd58f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F225023_342d9920b474b2acd20c011c74bdd58f.jpg&h=0372d5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0M6Y810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0M6Y810.jpg&h=3b8d34dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3a2260b21fd1921c6d46b5a6af6994d7e64c997","tid":108870,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"幫你推吓　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e6bfd15f7b346523459016bd7fd66490ff7619","tid":108870,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你推吓　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef7161b70ea8cd74c2ec5b28f479f19717f8151","tid":108870,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"MG-1行5.6v<br />\n你粒LR44 1.5，CR123A 3.0<br />\n都唔夠力點推，你試下上網搵點塞四粒LR44仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n唔使入菲林試喇<br />\nYashica呢堆機全部行電子快門控制，得A mode<br />\n你一日搞唔掂個測光，部機唔會用得到"},{"pid":"6998b85e0bdd7a11aa37a0cf1767408b2d1cc169","tid":108870,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MG-1行5.6v<br />\n你粒LR44 1.5，CR123A 3.0<br />\n都唔夠力點推，你試下上網搵點塞四粒LR44仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n唔使入菲林試喇<br />\nYashica呢堆機全部行電子快門控制，得A mode<br />\n你一日搞唔掂個測光，部機唔會用得到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我再試下搵個adapter 睇下點先啦<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為擺左好耐無搞過<br />\n驚佢都係唔得<br />\n巴打有無整相機嘅介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8433cc6de097a311e3fa1fddc0840089fcb0caaa","tid":108870,"uid":35021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"樓主可以度一度4LR44長度 fit 唔 fit到落去，網上有專用adaptor但比較貴，6V同5.6V差距唔會太遠，頂多0.3EV"},{"pid":"4d6f509f713f650e1d2da91110b1695d45303884","tid":108870,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可以度一度4LR44長度 fit 唔 fit到落去，網上有專用adaptor但比較貴，6V同5.6V差距唔會太遠，頂多0.3EV</blockquote><br />\n試左喇都唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係唔係真係壞左呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f4868768be2893a1a9c6a78212442f9a56aaf0","tid":108870,"uid":74109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9t2FKJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9t2FKJW.jpg&h=9e99ed18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講開4lr44，我多數都係自己整<br />\n4粒lr44、膠紙，錫紙 就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdf5cc645ee79c073efa2587beb5b404b3af899","tid":108870,"uid":74109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"樓主可以睇埋電池接觸位有無生鏽呀銅綠呀之類，搵個螺絲批鳩刮下有時都有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36a2560b0d3776a59d32bf1fd68a6ac84056ade","tid":108870,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可以睇埋電池接觸位有無生鏽呀銅綠呀之類，搵個螺絲批鳩刮下有時都有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來用錫紙就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好呀 我試下儘我所能清潔左佢先啦<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}